{"tid":1928810,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"歐美留學生返港","createTime":"2020-03-16T14:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:02:27.000Z","uid":252042,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"097a1ee9b17370b6c9091f06ca7592458f3f1d3f","tid":1928810,"uid":252042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"呢一期有極大量留學生返過嚟香港，依家香港對上嗰幾十單確診都係來自大量嘅海外既人，返香港嘅機票基本上係爆曬，勁多人一齊返嚟<br />\n<br />\n如果返緊嚟既留學生見到呢個post嘅話，唔該做好自己家居隔離，唔好出街玩<br />\n<br />\n香港人自己要注意身邊有冇呢啲人，要提醒佢哋做返好自己嘅本分<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arJh0zR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarJh0zR.jpg&h=b4fa046c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2Yh0zU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2Yh0zU.jpg&h=543e1fa7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acbd4a275d4170683298ba6e70d0d6a852f0fefc","tid":1928810,"uid":252042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"5cb3ce41347c68b79c20c82e069265168ff0188c","tid":1928810,"uid":252042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:57:15.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"f5e6c699ebbc92d3d8215b3f9b36f43ae703e5e9","tid":1928810,"uid":252042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"31ca5412b8a2a52387301871f6b8d3efe38ab273","tid":1928810,"uid":252042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"c9ca529f6f575dd235a17982d81dae6439dee42a","tid":1928810,"uid":353267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">基本上休息一兩日 就落lkf</span></span>"},{"pid":"05a2b4eff2d44839f3181c84c1fffc402d02863c","tid":1928810,"uid":252042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"5aed7358988ecc3a6148ef5239625bf30837